trad_vars <- read_fst("application_outcome_loan_aggregators.fst",as.data.table = T)
outcome_summary <- trad_vars[source == "Loan aggregator" & !is.na(outcome) & cs_bin %in% 620:800 & pull_date>="2018-01-01",.(no_of_applications=.N),by=.(source,cs_bin,order,outcome)]
outcome_summary[,tot:=sum(no_of_applications),by=cs_bin]
outcome_summary[,pct_apps:=no_of_applications/tot]
setorder(outcome_summary,cs_bin,order)

loans <- read_fst(path="/home/dimuthu/SSRN Oct 2021/Predictability/loans.fst",as.data.table = T)
loans[,sq_monthly_income:=sqrt(annual_income/12)]

loans[,huntington_rejected:=ifelse((fico_score>=690 & fico_score<740 & dti<35 & loan_amount<=25000) |

                                  )]

formula_basic <- as.formula(paste0("delinquent12~",paste(c("fico_score","log(1+number_of_accounts)","sq_monthly_income","dti","loan_amount","log(1+inquiries_past_6_months)","dti","loan_amount"),collapse = "+")))

loans[,source:=ifelse(utm_source2 %in% c("Lending Tree","Credit Karma","Nerdwallet","The Penny Hoarder"),"Loan aggregator",ifelse(utm_source2 %in% c("Facebook","Google"),"online advertisement",ifelse(utm_source2=="Direct","Direct",NA)))]
